"Leigh-Ann supported me as EA and Investor Relations coordinator at Ascend Wellness Holdings during a period of significant operational growth. She managed stakeholder relationships across seven markets and kept investor communications running smoothly for a publicly traded, multi-state cannabis operation. What stood out was her ability to operate in a highly regulated, fast-moving environment without missing a beat. Board preparation, investor updates, compliance-sensitive communications. She handled it all with professionalism and discretion. Leigh-Ann is the kind of executive partner who makes the entire leadership team more effective."

---

Here's the direct link to leave the recommendation on LinkedIn:
${linkedinRecommendationUrl}

No pressure at all. I appreciate everything, John.

Best,
Leigh-Ann`
