  {
    name: "Abner Kurtin",
    title: "Executive Chairman & Founder",
    company: "Ascend Wellness Holdings",
    relationship: "Leigh-Ann worked with Abner in his capacity as founder and Executive Chairman, supporting board-level operations, governance, and investor relations.",
    email: "abner.kurtin@awholdings.com",
    altEmails: [],
    recommendation: `Leigh-Ann was a key part of our executive operations at Ascend Wellness Holdings. As founder and Chairman, I needed someone who could handle board-level communications, investor relations, and sensitive operational matters with complete professionalism. Leigh-Ann delivered on all of it. She managed relationships with 200+ stakeholders across our multi-state operation and brought a level of organization to our board processes that raised the standard for the entire team. Her background spanning Big Four accounting to biotech gave her a rare versatility. She understands how executive offices operate at the highest level.`,
    emailSubject: "Reaching out with a quick ask",
    emailBody: `Hi Abner,

I hope you're well. I wanted to reach out because I'm growing my fractional executive support practice and your perspective would carry a lot of weight.

Working with you at Ascend gave me the chance to support board operations and investor relations at a level I'm really proud of. A LinkedIn recommendation from you would help prospective clients understand the caliber of work I deliver.

I've put together a draft below to make it easy. Please feel free to use it as-is, adjust it, or write something in your own words.

Here's the draft:

---

"Leigh-Ann was a key part of our executive operations at Ascend Wellness Holdings. As founder and Chairman, I needed someone who could handle board-level communications, investor relations, and sensitive operational matters with complete professionalism. Leigh-Ann delivered on all of it. She managed relationships with 200+ stakeholders across our multi-state operation and brought a level of organization to our board processes that raised the standard for the entire team. Her background spanning Big Four accounting to biotech gave her a rare versatility. She understands how executive offices operate at the highest level."

---

Here's the direct link to leave the recommendation on LinkedIn:
${linkedinRecommendationUrl}

Thank you, Abner. I truly appreciate it.

Best,
Leigh-Ann`
