    relationship: "Leigh-Ann worked with Frank across real estate expansion strategy, cross-functional coordination, and executive operations during the company's rapid growth phase.",
    email: "frank.perullo@awholdings.com",
    altEmails: [],
    recommendation: `Leigh-Ann was essential to keeping executive operations running at Ascend Wellness during one of our most intense growth periods. She coordinated across departments, managed complex scheduling for a leadership team operating in multiple states, and maintained an investor relations function that our stakeholders consistently praised. What I valued most was her ability to work independently at a high level. You could hand Leigh-Ann a complex project with moving parts and trust that it would be executed flawlessly. She brings real strategic thinking to executive support, not just task management.`,
    emailSubject: "A favor from your former colleague",
