I hope things are going well. I wanted to reach out because I'm building my fractional executive support business, and a LinkedIn recommendation from someone who saw my work at Ascend up close would mean a lot.

You experienced firsthand how I managed cross-functional coordination, investor relations, and executive operations during that intense growth period. Your perspective would be really valuable.

I've drafted something below to save you the blank-page problem. Feel free to use it, edit it, or write something completely different.

