"Leigh-Ann was essential to keeping executive operations running at Ascend Wellness during one of our most intense growth periods. She coordinated across departments, managed complex scheduling for a leadership team operating in multiple states, and maintained an investor relations function that our stakeholders consistently praised. What I valued most was her ability to work independently at a high level. You could hand Leigh-Ann a complex project with moving parts and trust that it would be executed flawlessly. She brings real strategic thinking to executive support, not just task management."

