I hope everything is going well. I'm reaching out because I've been growing my fractional executive support practice, and a LinkedIn recommendation from you would be really helpful.

We worked together on the operations side at Ascend during a period of rapid expansion, and your perspective would carry a lot of credibility. I've put together a draft below to make it easy.

Feel free to use it as written, adjust it, or write something entirely your own. Whatever works for you.

Here's the draft:

